OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1781175772
OL,3,CManchester United confirm the release
OL,4,Cof #73 million signing Jadon Sancho
OL,6,FManchester United have confirmed the
OL,7,Frelease of England winger Jadon Sancho.
OL,9,FThe 24-year-old signed from Borussia
OL,10,FDortmund for #73 million in July 2021
OL,11,Famid huge expectations but has spent
OL,12,Fthe last three seasons out on loan.
OL,14,FHis career at Manchester United
OL,15,Fstalled after a public disagreement
OL,16,Fwith then-manager Erik ten Hag
OL,17,Ffollowing his omission from the squad
OL,18,Fto face Arsenal in August 2023.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
