OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1781175772
OL,3,CManchester United confirm the release
OL,4,Cof #73 million signing Jadon Sancho
OL,6,FSince then, apart from a brief cameo
OL,7,Fin the 2024 Community Shield, Sancho
OL,8,Fhas not featured for United.
OL,10,FChelsea decided to avoid buying Sancho
OL,11,Fafter his loan in 2024-25. He then
OL,12,Fjoined Aston Villa, where he only
OL,13,Fstarted nine league games in his year
OL,14,Fplaying for Unai Emery.
OL,16,FHis time at Aston Villa ended in a
OL,17,FEuropa League triumph in May 2026.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
