OL,3,CManchester United confirm the release
OL,4,Cof #73 million signing Jadon Sancho
OL,6,FSancho has played in a European final
OL,7,Ffor each of his three loan clubs,
OL,8,FBorussia Dortmund, Chelsea, and Aston
OL,9,FVilla, each in a different competition.
OL,11,FWednesday's announcement ends months
OL,12,Fof speculation about his future away
OL,13,Ffrom Old Trafford.
OL,15,FUnited's decision to let Sancho go
OL,16,Fbrings the curtain down on the tenure
OL,17,Fof the fourth most expensive signing
OL,18,Fin the club's history.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
